But feel free to change any of the settings!</p>

<dl class="dictionary">
	<dt id="src">src</dt>
	<dd>The path to your “<a href="<:url "support/organization/src/":>">src</a>” directory, relative to the project root.</dd>
</dl>

<dl class="dictionary">
	<dt id="autoload">autoload</dt>
	<dd>The path to your “<a href="<:url "support/organization/lens/autoload.php/":>">autoload.php</a>” file, relative to the project root.</dd>
</dl>

<dl class="dictionary">
	<dt id="cache">cache</dt>
	<dd>The path to your “<a href="<:url "support/organization/lens/cache/":>">cache</a>” directory, relative to the project root.</dd>
</dl>

<dl class="dictionary">
	<dt id="checkForUpdates">checkForUpdates</dt>
	<dd>If <samp>true</samp>, Lens will let you know when it’s time to upgrade.</dd>
</dl>

<dl class="dictionary">
	<dt id="mockClasses">mockClasses</dt>
	<dd>A list of classes that Lens should mock.</dd>
</dl>

<dl class="dictionary">
	<dt id="mockFunctions">mockFunctions</dt>
	<dd>A list of functions that Lens should mock.</dd>
